Authorised Persons must maintain accurate and comprehensive records to demonstrate adherence to UAE AML/CFT Federal Laws and the FSRA's AML Rules, as outlined in the regulatory requirements. These records must be kept up-to-date and readily available for review or audit by the FSRA (FSMR sections 201 and 206). Specifically, Authorised Persons are expected to:

